{"tid":1028139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國300年酒莊被中国買家改名「御兔」   法國人：好笑又難以置信","createTime":"2019-02-19T09:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T11:29:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5256867b74b4865904d5a7c102d8b97d2a9ed6","tid":1028139,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/19/realtime/5943161.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F19%2Frealtime%2F5943161.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=6396b64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國波爾多地區諸多酒莊被中國大陸買家購入並改名，比如有300年歷史的「藝術之源」酒莊改名「御兔」，此前還有品牌被改名為「藏羚羊」。當地居民覺得好笑又難以置信。波爾多地區阿爾韋爾市副市長稱非常遺憾：「這標誌着我們地區部分歷史的消失」。<br />\n<br />\n大陸官媒《環球時報》引述法國電視二台報導，從2011年以來，中國已經成為波爾多地區葡萄酒排名第一的進口國，愈來愈多的買家熱衷購買酒莊並為其改名。當地居民覺得好笑又難以置信。一位受訪者說，以後說不定還會出現「金龍」酒莊。<br />\n<br />\n法國作家索萊爾曾專門向時任波爾多市長的法國前總理朱佩寫信，表達酒莊改名的現象的不滿。他說：「我很震驚這些名字得到波爾多市政府的認可。從小在波爾多長大的我，從未見過皇家兔子或者藏羚羊的一根毫毛。我不知道藏羚羊與波爾多紅酒有甚麼聯繫，但我很惋惜，這些擁有幾個世紀歷史的葡萄酒酒莊變成了一種中國民俗的大雜燴。」<br />\n<br />\n不過波爾多葡萄酒行業協會副主席法爾日認為，改名並不會損害波爾多葡萄酒的聲譽，毋須小題大做。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，波爾多地區有6,000多家酒莊，其中已有140家被中國大陸商人收購。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3651949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F3651949&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ9TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=c9d4e1bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3651949</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php9Y94UG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php9Y94UG.jpg&h=71a2c24e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35b16398afc66a0185e24aee0f7d346259808d7c","tid":1028139,"uid":58374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"條路自己揀"},{"pid":"357ae71ade288e535782e32eeb0b3818452f9c0e","tid":1028139,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"Lapin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3fa2bd53314f62b8419f063283fb8b0d0f50af","tid":1028139,"uid":6334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thedrinksbusiness.com/2017/12/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AF%8C%E5%95%86%E6%9B%B4%E5%90%8D%E6%B3%A2%E5%B0%94%E5%A4%9A%E9%85%92%E5%BA%84%E5%BC%95%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedrinksbusiness.com%2F2017%2F12%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%25AF%258C%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25B0%2594%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2584%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%258B%2585%25E5%25BF%25A7%2F&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ9TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=471bd79e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thedrinksbusiness.com/2017/12/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AF%8C%E5%95%86%E6%9B%B4%E5%90%8D%E6%B3%A2%E5%B0%94%E5%A4%9A%E9%85%92%E5%BA%84%E5%BC%95%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%A7/</a><br />\n17年12月既新聞..."},{"pid":"1eb28d73bf984a3abb580fc8b13d0fa7acc54b79","tid":1028139,"uid":52459,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"祖業守唔住，發國佬無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4227824b8e1c392cc98fd5a04579f99f3f66d37","tid":1028139,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"「有間酒莊」"},{"pid":"5e320a2cc52b16c7887a898190888f102ee9ee47","tid":1028139,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"見習酒莊"},{"pid":"c4548dcceb0a2ecb5398ab59fb8a607f23dc5640","tid":1028139,"uid":19183,"like":0,"dislike"